headline: TELUS to Acquire Remaining TELUS Digital Shares in $539 Million Deal
summary: TU announces a $2.9B deal to fully acquire TELUS Digital, unlocking AI, SaaS and global growth opportunities across key industries.

headline: 5 Low-Beta Defensive Stocks to Bank on as Consumer Confidence Shrinks
summary: With consumer confidence waning, ATO, FTS, NWN, INGR and CSV stand out as low-beta defensive plays with growth and dividend strength.
